			Keyboard	
			Configure Keyboard 
			by Guido Schimmels

13-Apr-2008 (Version 0.11.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~

See svn log for details.

Changes in release 0.11:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- Added a test area for trying out the new settings (Thomas Leonard).

- Added more tooltips (Thomas Leonard).

- Updated documentation (Thomas Leonard).

- Rearranged layout to save some space (Thomas Leonard).

- Removed text on setting ROX-Filer short-cuts (Thomas Leonard).


06-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.10.1)

No need for garbage collection when changing these options (Tony Houghton).

04-Oct-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.10.0)

New generic settings.py, compatible with dbus 0.36 bindings (Tony Houghton).

25-Apr-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.4)

Compatible with dbus 0.32 bindings (Tony Houghton).


21-Jan-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.3)

Option for enabling NumLock/CapsLock/ScrollLock at login.
	
16-Jul-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.2)

Added options for keyboard auto-repeat; see also ROX-Session (Tony
Houghton).

04-June-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9.1)

Implemented XKB keyboard layout switching as XSetting for ROX-Session
Users, please remove SetXKBMap from your Autostart directory!

01-June-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.9)

Support for XKB keyboard layout switching

03-May-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.8.1)

Fix XDG support.

02-May-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~

(Version 0.8)
Created a first, fully functional version.

